completely
kicked out of the Olympic Games.

21:40.833 --> 21:45.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But that's only two weeks before
Rio. I think
what we could see happening is
many more Russian

21:45.137 --> 21:48.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
