they're guilty.

21:50.743 --> 21:53.812 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: We have got less than
a minute
left, and we have got all sorts
of issues

21:53.846 --> 21:55.648 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
surrounding the Rio Olympics.

21:55.681 --> 21:59.919 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
