you have got
this. Is there a big cloud
that's going to

22:04.323 --> 22:05.591 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
be over these Games?

22:05.624 --> 22:07.359 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHRISTINE BRENNAN: There could
be unlike any
other Olympics.

22:07.393 --> 22:10.596 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Usually, there's always
something that you
think about, terrorism in Sochi
or terrorism

22:10.629 --> 22:15.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Athens, a home game for the
terrorists
at the Olympics in Athens in
'04, and then

22:15.601 --> 22:17.403 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
nothing bad happens.

22:17.436 --> 22:21.740 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The question here is maybe will
