the case, but I think Rio might
really be

22:29.915 --> 22:32.918 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that first Olympic city to have
real trouble
hosting the Games.

22:32.952 --> 22:35.120 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Two months away. We
will see what
happens.

22:35.154 --> 22:41.126 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Christine Brennan, thanks so
much for being
with us.

22:41.160 --> 22:47.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
CHRISTINE BRENNAN: Thank you,
John.

22:47.666 --> 22:55.774 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Coming up on the
"NewsHour": Venezuelans
hit their breaking point as food
