science teachers.

28:49.728 --> 28:52.264 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH SEAMANDS, Wright Junior
Senior High
School: One guy teaches 7th and
8th grade.

28:52.297 --> 28:55.901 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
