11 and 12.

28:55.934 --> 28:58.170 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Have you guys converted Celsius
to kelvins?

28:58.203 --> 29:02.474 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Small schools like
Sarah Seamands'
can't support having specialists
to teach

29:02.507 --> 29:06.178 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
