that's how I
feel.

29:37.142 --> 29:42.280 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: With the new
standards, teachers
like Seamands will have to
change not in one

29:42.314 --> 29:44.082 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
subject, but four.

29:44.116 --> 29:50.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH SEAMANDS: They have just
told us it's
coming, that it's in -- it's on
its way, and

29:50.088 --> 29:53.191 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
be prepared, because things are
going to change.

29:53.225 --> 29:58.196 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Ready or not,
Wyoming is on
the verge of adopting the new
standards statewide,

29:58.230 --> 30:01.833 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
but with one big exception.

30:01.867 --> 30:06.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is coal country, and
